The paper is about a machine learning algorithm for keyword spotting, which is a subfield of speech recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound). The paper also involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which are covered by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The algorithm is designed for embedded systems, which suggests a focus on system design and optimization, falling under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
